    "title": "Improve new tab accessibility",
    "body": "<!-- CURSOR_AGENT_PR_BODY_BEGIN -->\n## 変更点\n- タスクリストと完了履歴にローカライズ済みの accessible name を追加\n- 入力欄へ移動する空状態ボタンに `aria-controls` を追加\n- フォーカスリングを強化し、キーボード操作時のフォーカス位置を見やすく調整\n- 操作ボタン、テーマカラー入力、リンクのタップ領域を 48px 以上に拡大\n- 主要テキスト/操作境界色のコントラストを WCAG AA 相当に改善\n\n## build通過\n- `npm run build` 通過\n- `npm run lint` 通過\n\n## permissions不変\n- `manifest.json` は未変更\n- permissions / host_permissions の追加なし\n<!-- CURSOR_AGENT_PR_BODY_END -->\n\n<div><a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents/bc-c11d388d-fd0a-42df-ad67-2c26c1fc97d8\"><picture><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/open-in-web-dark.png\"><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/open-in-web-light.png\"><img alt=\"Open in Web\" width=\"114\" height=\"28\" src=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/open-in-web-dark.png\"></picture></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-c11d388d-fd0a-42df-ad67-2c26c1fc97d8\"><picture><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/open-in-cursor-dark.png\"><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/open-in-cursor-light.png\"><img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" width=\"131\" height=\"28\" src=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/open-in-cursor-dark.png\"></picture></a>&nbsp;</div>\n\n",
